parameters:
Bunny-chan: On behalf of the Monster Fight management, we
have officially accepted the rematch between Lord Shark and
Anomalocaris Mosman♪ From now on, Lord Shark will undertake
the tasks that are a condition for the rematch❤︎

Bunny-chan: So, Lord Shark♪ From here on out, you'll be
going around the city naked while masturbating. We've set up
a course that we believe to be appropriate!

Memimi: (The underground district... in front of the
station, the shopping district... It's all major roads...!
This route, gah... it even goes right in front of the
school... Seriously, everyone in the city might end up
seeing this...)

Anomalocaris Mosman: What's wrong, you look pale? Drop the
bravado, maybe you should just give up on the rematch? This
could really be the end of everything...

Memimi: ...Fuhahaha, how kind of you! Unfortunately, I'm not
so delicately wired as to run away blushing from something
like this. And yet you imagine my naked body with such
vulgar anticipation, don't hold back on my account!!

Memimi: (Ahhh ahhhh... Gosh, I keep saying too much... Am I
really going to do this today...? In front of tens of
thousands of people in the city, to masturbate...!? )

While nearly passing out from the overwhelming thought,
Memimi headed towards the starting point...
